# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# Node dependencies
node_modules/

# Yarn / PNPM / NPM artifacts
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# Build outputs (for all Next.js projects)
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/

# Environment files (keep local only)
**/.env
**/.env.*

# TypeScript build info
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/next-env.d.ts

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
*.log

# OS / IDE junk
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# Vercel / Deployment
.vercel/

# Coverage / Testing
coverage/
**/coverage/

# Misc / Security
*.pem
*.key
*.crt

# Local cache or runtime data
.tmp/
.cache/

# Optional: lockfiles for multi-package repos (if you use workspaces)
# Uncomment if each app manages its own lockfile
# **/package-lock.json
# **/yarn.lock
# **/pnpm-lock.yaml
.idea